<BR><DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c6"><SPAN CLASS="c7">Sound Off! April 30</SPAN></P>
</DIV>
<BR><DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c6"><SPAN CLASS="c8">BYLINE: </SPAN><SPAN CLASS="c2">Sun-News report</SPAN></P>
</DIV>
